<DocsLayout
  title="Runs Not Appearing"
  description="Troubleshoot missing scenario runs."
  prevPage={{ slug: "stats-folder", title: "Stats Folder Issues" }}
  nextPage={{ slug: "benchmark-issues", title: "Benchmark Issues" }}
>
  <h2>New Runs Not Showing Up</h2>
  <p>
    If you've played scenarios but they're not appearing in RefleK's, try these
    steps:
  </p>

  <h2>Check the Stats Folder</h2>
  <ol>
    <li>Open Settings → General → Stats Folder</li>
    <li>Verify the path is correct</li>
    <li>Open the folder in File Explorer</li>
    <li>Check that new CSV files are being created when you play</li>
  </ol>

  <h2>Restart RefleK's</h2>
  <p>Sometimes the file watcher needs a reset:</p>
  <ol>
    <li>Close RefleK's completely (check the system tray)</li>
    <li>Reopen RefleK's</li>
    <li>Play a scenario and check if it appears</li>
  </ol>

  <h2>Check KovaaK's Settings</h2>
  <p>Make sure KovaaK's is configured to save stats:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Open KovaaK's settings</li>
    <li>Verify that stats saving is enabled</li>
    <li>Check that CSV format is selected</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>File Permissions</h2>
  <p>If RefleK's can't read the stats folder:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Run RefleK's as administrator (right-click → Run as administrator)</li>
    <li>Check that the stats folder isn't read-only</li>
    <li>Make sure antivirus isn't blocking access</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="note">
    <strong>Still stuck?</strong> Join our <a
      href="https://discord.gg/SFsf4GQhJU"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer">Discord server</a
    > or <a
      href="https://github.com/ARm8-2/refleks/issues"
      target="_blank"
